messages.text: Hey man, what’s up?
Yo
Not much, wanna hang ?
Yep: I’m in the subway now from downtown.
Come over, play FIFA
Will do, see you in 10
kk
Dude, something is going down.
What ?
There’s a fight between two guys in the train.
Jump in!
They’re really serious
Oh they’re punching each other badly!
Ok I’m going in.
Careful man
Shit, one has a knife!
What?
He’s threatening the other guy.
What? Get out of there!
Wait I’m filming for evidence
Dude, get out of there! why do you care?
waiting for the stop. Call police.
Man the connection was so bad, I couldn’t hear a word you were saying.
One of the guy is stabbed!!!
I’m with him now. Try calling back.
Dude, connection is too bad I can’t get through.
Ok, I’m with the guy that’s been stabbed, help me!
Where’s the other guy? Are u ok?
He ran away to another subway car
Tell me what to do! He is bleeding a lot
Wait for 911
Dude someone pulled the alarm, we’re stuck on the rails.
They won’t be here in time! I’m freaking out.
Ok, OK, let me call 911, They’ll tell me what to do.
Ok, hurry.
Ok, so the woman from 911 asks, where is he stabbed ?
Stomach
Be more specific please
Um, lower abdominals on the right, like on his right v line.
Don’t know exact term.
Ok, is it bleeding a lot ?
Yeah, my hands are covered, hard to type.
Ok, is there anyone else with you ?
No, everyone fled the other way, I’m alone in the car.
man
OK, you need to press with something like a piece of tissue
Ok, I took off my shirt, I’m pressing on the wound with it.
Is he conscious ?
Yeah
He has to hold still. She says you should reassure the victim.
That’s common sense dude! of course I’m doing that!
Sorry, I know.
They’re sending help.
They are people trying to access the train. Paramedics I mean
Great, he’s scared man.
Keep him awake.
Ok might have to put the phone down.
Ok man, I’m following this live with the girl from 911.
They should be there any second.
You there?
The woman says they got it from there, that they got him, confirm ?
Sorry, yeah, they got him
Need a second, I’m shaking badly.
Adrenaline going down.
The woman says you should inhale in a bag or something.
You’ll be fine
It’s ok, paramedics are calming me.
Man, what the fuck? What a fucking crazy story!
Haha, I know
Dude, do you realize what you have just done?
Woman says you saved his life
He would have bled out without you.
Will he be ok ?
They’ll update us later, don’t know yet.
But she says the paramedic told her they were confident!
Dude, you’re a fucking hero, Do you realize you’re the only one that stayed and helped this guy?
Couldn’t have done it without you, thx
Shut up! You did it all! Dude, I’m so proud, I want to hug you so badly right now.
SO. Much. Adrenaline !!
I know, I feel so weird like excited and about to pass out at the same time.
That was so intense!
Will take a cab. Ready to have your ass kicked in FIFA?
HAHA You crazy motherfucker!
I love you bro! get over here, let’s celebrate !
Will be there soon
Love you too (still manly if over the phone right?)
We’re way past that dude!
